name: .GB4 File Extension
summary: Learn about .GB4 files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: You can open a GB4 file in the paid version of Geekbench 4 Pro (cross-platform). (You cannot open a GB4 file in any other version of Geekbench Pro.) To do so, open the GUI version of Geekbench 4 Pro and select File â†’ Open.... Then, navigate to and select your GB4 file. The results your GB4 file contains will appear in Geekbench 4 Pro.

If you do not have access to Geekbench 4 Pro, you can also open your GB4 file in any text editor, such as Microsoft Notepad (Windows) or Apple TextEdit (Mac). This will allow you to view the plain text used to show your test results in Geekbench 4 Pro.
